Busuu is a platform for self learning that empowers people through languages. Whether you’re learning for a new job, new love or simply a new skill, your path to fluency starts here. Our combination of self-paced study: complete your personalized Study Plan, and get friendly reminders when it’s time to learn and benefit from the smart technology in our review section, which highlights what to revise and when. And all that by practicing with 120 million native speakers around the world by sharing knowledge together, correcting the work of others, and having your exercises reviewed in return whenever you want to. Self-paced studying works because you’re in control.